original_title: Raise Up: The World Is Our Gym
overview: An underground urban fitness movement risks losing its identity as a social tool as it becomes the fastest growing new sport. Born on the streets of NYC, cultures clash between the old school and the young blood as the movement transitions from city parks to stadiums all over the world.
tagline: The evolution of an urban fitness phenomenon... from city streets to stadiums around the world!
title: Raise Up: The World Is Our Gym
